Why am I searched so thoroughly ?
#HINT#
13

#TEXT#
For one reason, there's an important document missing.
#FINISH#
#HINT#
13

#TEXT#
For another, they know the American agent had it.
#FINISH#
#HINT#
13

#TEXT#
You are American, therefore somewhat suspicious.
