Why am I followed at the station ?
#HINT#
20

#TEXT#
Clearly, you are under suspicion.
#FINISH#
#HINT#
20

#TEXT#
There are a number of things you may have done to make the situation worse. 
See the previous two questions. Also, if the guards found anything peculiar in their 
search of your possessions, that would increase their suspicions.
#FINISH#
