Who is my contact ?
#HINT#
35

#TEXT#
It depends on what the American agent said at the very beginning.
#FINISH#
#HINT#
35

#TEXT#
Check your Frobnian phrase book (in your Border Zone package) for the 
translation of the phrase that your contact was supposed to repeat. Be careful; the 
exact words must be used.
#FINISH#
#HINT#
35

#TEXT#
When your contact appears, you must SAY "It is my fault" in Frobnian. Check your 
phrase book for the translation.
#FINISH#
#HINT#
35

#TEXT#
Then, GIVE THE COLOR ROLL TO THE CONTACT. Alternatively, you can 
DROP THE COLOR FILM; this latter method is less obvious, in case you are 
followed. Depending on how much suspicion you have raised, you may be able to 
do either, both, or none of these two things.
#FINISH#
