How can I avoid the searchlights?
#HINT#
90

#TEXT#
If you are not WATCHing them, you should.
#FINISH#
#HINT#
90

#TEXT#
The status line will show you the current positions of the lights.
#FINISH#
#HINT#
90

#TEXT#
You should plan to head NORTH when the three lights are all aimed away from 
you.
#FINISH#
#HINT#
90

#TEXT#
Make sure you understand where YOU are in relation to the three lights; the right 
times to cross differ depending on your position.
#FINISH#
#HINT#
90

#TEXT#
To cross successfully, you must be in good physical condition.
#FINISH#
#HINT#
90

#TEXT#
That means warm and not bleeding.
#FINISH#
#HINT#
90

#TEXT#
You should also be wearing proper shoes.
#FINISH#
#HINT#
90

#TEXT#
For example, the WORK SHOES in the hut
#FINISH#
